## Tools

### find_module(query)
Search wiki pages by keyword. Returns matching wiki page paths.
Index: {{ wiki_dir }}/INDEX.md

### get_symbol(id)
Look up a component by ID (format: `file::Class.method`).
Index: .indexer/manifest.json → files[*].component_ids

### trace_callers(symbol_id)
Find what calls a given symbol.
Source: relevant wiki page → Relationships → Called by

### what_changed(since_commit)
List files changed since a commit with their wiki pages.
Source: .indexer/manifest.json → last_indexed_commit + git log

### entry_points()
List all architectural entry points across the codebase.
Source: {{ wiki_dir }}/INDEX.md → Entry Points column
